mel , without guilt extorts great sums of money form all sides of the drug industry .
he plays tony off of frank until it catches up with him in a scene that marks the exit from the film of both frank and mel .
it is priceless to hear frank asking for mel to intercede , as tony is about to kill him only to hear mel reply , ` it 's your tree frank , you 're sitting in it . '
