the musical underscore is also quite effective , moody , featuring wordless female voice over a small orchestral ensemble ( too bad little if any of that made it onto shakti 's soundtrack cd , but bollywood has n't yet discovered the value of including score along with songs on their soundtrack albums , at least not in most cases ) .
