the film was begun in britain , but wartime difficulties made korda move it to southern california , which probably explains the presence of american ingram in the cast .
the art direction , in vibrant technicolor , is most attractive , especially the fairy tale architecture in blues , whites & pinks.*************************born sabu dastagir in 1924 , sabu was employed in the maharaja of mysore 's stables when he was discovered by korda 's company and set before the cameras .
his first four films ( elephant boy-1937 , the drum-1938 , the thief of bagdad-1940 , jungle book-1942 ) were his best and he found himself working out of hollywood when they were completed .
after distinguished military service in world war ii he resumed his film career , but he became endlessly confined for years playing ethnic roles in undistinguished minor films , black narcissus ( 1947 ) being the one great exception .
his final movie , walt disney 's a tiger walks ( 1964 ) was an improvement , but it was too late .
