basically , the plot of the movie is that rob roy borrows money from the marquis of montrose to buy cattle which he then intends to sell and reap a large profit from .
but , his plan is foiled when the friend entrusted with the money is robbed of the cash and murdered in the forest .
our hero finds himself on the run after failing to settle the matter with the marquis , and mary , his wife , suffers a sadistic rape at the hands of archibald cunningham , a smarmy englishman with no soul .
atrocities ensue , until , in an immensely satisfying conclusion , rob carves archibald up like a christmas turkey .
