nasty arlington decides to resolve matters by ambushing and shooting the ape - man and then telling jane and holt that tarzan was attacked and eaten by a crocodile .
of course , tarzan is n't deadonly wounded ; after being nursed back to health by cheetah ( ! ) , he swings back into action just in time to rescue jane from a tribe of vicious lion - eating savages who have attacked holt 's expedition .
tarzan and his mate , the second movie to star weismuller as the jungle man of few words , is often cited by fans as the best of the series ; although i slightly prefer the original , i can definitely understand the film 's popularity : it 's damn sexy and there are some great action sequences !
