he 's trying to atone for his sins - yes , gary did attempt suicide after the initial doc was aired - through correction , commentary , and convention , reclaiming such hollywood - narrative standbys as the best friend and the defiant happy ending ( two different ones , with a telling adjustment in the glover version ) and turning them to his own very personal uses .
